      "body" : "@rebroad 300 MB of memory usage; it corresponds to approximately 150 MB worth of actual block data (CTxMemPoolEntry uses much more memory than just the serialized transaction), or one day worth of blocks. Given a daily peak and trough of transaction volume, this is the minimum needed to get low-fee transaction in with some chance within a day.",
